{
  "stem": "14060.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had no reason [? not to. ?] And we had the shower.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then when we finished, we were lining up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody got a packet, more or less the striped uniform with the cap, you know, the [? mitza ?], they called it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you had your own shoes and some sort of underwear-- I can't even remember what it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No, no, no-- there was no underwear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was it, I think.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, all right-- we were lined up and taken into-- after the shower, into a barrack.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a huge, big barrack, very little windows on it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in the middle was like a brick-built-- like, a little oven-looking thing, but a low brick division, more or less, in the middle, if you like.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It must have been about a meter wide and about 75 centimeters high.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You could sit down on it, if you wanted, not that anybody would.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They pushed into that barrack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was [GERMAN SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That means the gypsy camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because there were different numbers of camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "One was the [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "A lager. ?] The gypsy camp was basically the worst, as such.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because the gypsies were totally cruel people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were themselves deported.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But the Germans realized that so amongst the Jews, amongst any others, they used the most brutal type of people to carry out being a kapo or blockalteste.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Blockalteste means the guy who was in charge of the block.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was just as equally bad as, as the kapo.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There were some nicer people and some not so nice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But the Germans knew the method to what sort of people to use for what sort of job.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We got lined up in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
